      "title": "Wind farm at Poonagri, Mannar: Adani Group gets approval",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister Kanchana Wijesekara has said that Adani Green Energy has been given approval for two wind farm projects worth more than US$ 500 million, with a capacity of 286 megawatts in Mannar and 234 megawatts in Poonagri."
      ],
